title: Grateful Dead Live at The Centrum on 1987-04-02
description:
Set 1

Cold Rain & Snow, Minglewood Blues, Dupree's Diamond Blues, Far From Me, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, When Push Comes To Shove, Beat It On Down The Line, Bird Song, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Looks Like Rain-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Space-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> The Wheel-> Black Peter-> Around & Around-> Good Lovin', E: Black Muddy River
